// Norwegian layout with brackets on ø/æ keys
// ø → (    Shift+ø → [    AltGr+ø → ø    AltGr+Shift+ø → Ø
// æ → )    Shift+æ → ]    AltGr+æ → æ    AltGr+Shift+æ → Æ
//
// Also handles Alt/Super swap + Left Cmd as Level3 (for @, etc.)
// Physical Option → Super (compositor mod)
// Physical Left Cmd → ISO_Level3_Shift (AltGr equivalent)
// Physical Right Cmd → ISO_Level3_Shift (AltGr, same as Left Cmd)

default partial alphanumeric_keys modifier_keys
xkb_symbols "basic" {
    include "no(mac)"

    key <AC10> { type = "FOUR_LEVEL", [ parenleft,  bracketleft,  oslash, Oslash ] };
    key <AC11> { type = "FOUR_LEVEL", [ parenright, bracketright, ae,     AE     ] };

    // Swap Alt/Super, both Cmd keys are Level3 (AltGr)
    key <LALT> { [ Super_L ] };
    key <RALT> { type[Group1] = "TWO_LEVEL", [ Super_R, Super_R ] };
    key <LWIN> { type[Group1] = "ONE_LEVEL", [ ISO_Level3_Shift ] };
    key <RWIN> { type[Group1] = "ONE_LEVEL", [ ISO_Level3_Shift ] };

    modifier_map Mod4 { <LALT>, <RALT> };
    modifier_map Mod5 { <LWIN>, <RWIN> };
};
